### [omega_params.py](file:///d:/DubaiMatrixASI/config/omega_params.py) — The Living Brain (478 linhas)

**Arquitetura: Auto-Mutating Parameter Space**

```mermaid
graph TD
    OP[OmegaParameter] --> |bounds enforcement| OPS[OmegaParameterSpace]
    OPS --> |thread-safe singleton| OMEGA["OMEGA (global)"]
    OMEGA --> |.get()| READ[Todos os subsistemas leem]
    OMEGA --> |.set() + reason| WRITE[SelfOptimizer / MutationEngine escrevem]
    OMEGA --> |.save()| DISK[omega_params.json]
    DISK --> |.load()| OMEGA
```

